    :match_1: deterministic|||A program that does the same thing every time it is run.
    :match_2: bottom-up design|||A method of program development that starts by writing small, useful functions and then assembling them into larger solutions.
    :match_3: histogram|||A vector of integers where each integer counts the number of values that fall into a certain range.

